value.name: Sugar Sugar Rune
value.overview: Chocolat Meilleure is a happy-going and optimistic girl. Together  with her friend-cum-rival, Vanilla Mieux, they are potential candidates  to become Queen of the magic world. After obtaining their magic wands,  they set off to the human world to gather the hearts of unsuspecting  humans. Whoever gets the most hearts will be the crowned Queen.
